Description: LANE CLOSURE INFO: Starting on February 18 2019 motorists can expect lane closures on Route 8 between I-95 in Bridgeport and Exit 14 in Shelton. Traffic control personnel and signing patterns will be utilized to guide motorists through the work zone. The regular work schedules for this project is 9:00 a.m. to 3:00 p.m. and 9:00 p.m. to 5:00 a.m. (Monday through Friday).
